				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/%E1%BA%A8n-gi%E1%BA%A3/poem-Z1S9KucXHucaFAlcHHXMcw">Ẩn giả - 隱者</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/C%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i-thi/poem-v156h-D_IlDqgWMKRRkKiw">Cảm hoài thi - 感懷詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-20/poem-H5YA0TL7lRbnfJqG7nExKg">Cảm ngộ kỳ 20 - 感遇其二十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/Ng%C5%A9-H%C3%A0nh-s%C6%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-lXg4pA8dwTL6zCyvWAl4HA">Ngũ Hành sơn kỳ 1 - 五行山其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-k7nDOMHcGKaZoky6ue8-ag">Nguyễn Thượng Hiền</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QwHBlDHxHjNmmwiMhPsXpg">Thu dạ lữ hoài ngâm - 秋夜旅懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Th%E1%BB%A9-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Khu%C3%AA-ti%E1%BB%85n-t%E1%BA%B7ng-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-O25H0eQ6jXpgPZKpzWiVzQ">Thứ Dương Khuê tiễn tặng nguyên vận - 次楊奎餞贈原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BA%BF-th%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-o_x0QvCv3dxXC8-Nyd0Leg">Thướng Bạch Đế thành nhị thủ kỳ 2 - 上白帝城二首其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/T%E1%BB%8Bch-th%E1%BB%A9-Chi-Ngh%C4%A9a-d%E1%BB%8Bch-v%C3%A3n-L%E1%BA%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-hi%E1%BB%87p-tr%E1%BA%A5n-T%C3%B4-Xuy%C3%AAn-h%E1%BA%A7u/poem-_W0oNSCYrVyuJaeugHf8bA">Tịch thứ Chi Nghĩa dịch, vãn Lạng Sơn hiệp trấn Tô Xuyên hầu - 夕佽芝義驛挽諒山協鎮蘇川侯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/author-YFWZ8afu7g2IoLevX1_E2Q">Nguyễn Đề</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Vi%E1%BB%85n-du-Giang-kho%C3%A1t-ph%C3%B9-cao-%C4%91%E1%BB%91ng/poem-G0i4dJiLIOYZivh8myuVSg">Viễn du (Giang khoát phù cao đống) - 遠遊（江闊浮高凍）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/Xu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-HGy-HiI_KT9QKZYpXPR_lA">Xuân hành - 春行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/author-zlEhGhvit8FPpDIsa8T0QA">Giả Đảo</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
